Lol how much of him you actually lane had to lane against? My guess not much. As a person who plays a lot of bot lane, unless you're lucky enough to have a great support, you aren't winning lane ever. It just isn't gonna happen. It isn't just a matter of overturned, as he also is, but his kit is just dumb. "I'm gonna pull you from a full screen away, knock you up, aoe nuke silence. Then I also have this shield that pops on for a 50% of my current mana. Now since you're low Imma speed away and pull you again. Meanwhile my ADC is melting you" 

You can make anyone sound OP when you say the things they're good at

